'''Jack Avon''' is a financial consultant and writer based in the United Kingdom. He is the author of ''The Handbook of Financial Modeling'' and ''The Basics of Financial Modeling'', published in New York in 2013 and 2014 respectively,<ref>{{cite web|title=The Handbook of Financial Modeling|url=http://www.apress.com/9781430262053|publisher=[[Apress]]|accessdate=26 February 2014}}</ref> and of ''The Bid Proposal Handbook'', published by in London in May 2017. His latest non-fiction book is ''The Interim Contractor'', published in London in 2017.<ref>{{cite web|title=The Interim Contractor|url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/Interim-Contractor-Jack-Avon-ebook/dp/B075CPNP28/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1508849054&sr=8-1&keywords=the+interim+contractor|publisher=[[Begawans Veranda]]|accessdate=14 September 2017}}</ref> Avon is a world expert in financial modelling.<ref>{{cite web|title=A Practical Approach to Creating and ...|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FPNZAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA11&lpg=PA11&dq=The+Handbook+of+Financial+Modeling&source=bl&ots=bQPdQQ3A_9&sig=aME2-Jkx9lweu1Ofrbcob_YmwtA&hl=en&sa=X&ei=VekNU4r8FITGrAetxoHQBQ&ved=0CG4Q6AEwCQ#v=onepage&q=The%20Handbook%20of%20Financial%20Modeling&f=false|publisher=[[Google Books]]|accessdate=26 February 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Financial Model Expert, Jack Avon, Teaches Business Professionals Tricks ...|url=http://www.prweb.com/releases/2014/01/prweb11496569.htm|publisher=[[Vocus (software)|Vocus]]|accessdate=26 February 2014}}</ref>

==Early life and education==
Jack Avon was born [[Lusaka]], the capital city of [[Zambia]], in March 1967, where he lived until he moved with his family to the United Kingdom in June 1976. In March 1977 he moved to Hong Kong with his family due to his father's work, spending a year in Hong Kong and attended [[Quarry Bay School]] and [[Peak School]]. In September 1978 he returned to the United Kingdom to attend [[Clayesmore Preparatory School]] in [[Iwerne Minster]], [[Dorset]] and then [[Clayesmore School]]. He completed his higher education at [[Bournemouth University]] and [[Royal Holloway, University of London]].{{citation needed|date=June 2017}}

In sport, Avon played rugby, [[field hockey]] and cricket and competed in athletics at Clayesmore School. He has played senior rugby at various clubs, including [[Bournemouth RFC]], [[Purley RFC]], [[Saracen FC]], [[HKFC]], [[Dorset & Wilts]], and [[HKRFU]]. In hockey Avon has played for [[Dorset and Wilts]], [[West of England]], [[Poole HC]], [[Valley Hockey, Hong Kong]], [[Surbiton HC]] and [[Wimbledon HC]].{{citation needed|date=June 2017}}

